**Professional Profile**
TRAN HOANG SON is a dedicated QA professional with 2 years of experience in the information technology industry, specializing in Software Testing and QA Analysis. They have a proven track record in developing automation scripts using Java and Selenium, performing functional, regression, and API testing, and reporting defects in Jira. The candidate has actively contributed to Agile Scrum teams, defining test cases and collaborating with developers to ensure quality for various platforms, including ad network management and AI-powered API systems. Notably, they have experience managing a small team within an Agile environment.

**Core Skills & Technology**
Java, Selenium, API Testing, Jira, Agile Scrum, Cucumber, JUnit, SQL, Black Box Testing, White Box Testing.

**Education & Certifications**
Holds a degree in Software Engineering from TON DUC THANG UNIVERSITY. Further enhancing their expertise, they are ISTQB Certified Tester Foundation Level and ISTQB Certified - Agile Tester, alongside a TOEIC Listening & Reading score of 845.